                                  Anchorage VAAC

   Why Volcanic Ash Advisory Centers?

        * A Boeing 747 will travel 9 miles every minute and 540 miles in an
          hour.
        * Volcanic ash clouds can cause jet engines to stall.
        * You want your pilot to know ASAP about volcanic eruptions and ash
          clouds ahead of your aircraft.
        * More info about Anchorage VAAC and the world wide Volcanic Ash
          Advisory program.

